##### MF4: ANGULAR DISTRIBUTIONS OF SECONDARY PARTICLES           2046 1451
                                                                  2046 1451
We use MF4 for the neutron scattering angular distribution for    2046 1451
discrete levels.                                                  2046 1451
                                                                  2046 1451
- MT2      : Elastic angular distribution                         2046 1451
                                                                  2046 1451
The flag LTT=3 is used to indicate a switch at some high energy,  2046 1451
generally 50 MeV, from a Legendre representation to a tabulated   2046 1451
representation. For incident energies below this energy, the      2046 1451
Legendre coefficients are given on a sufficiently precise energy  2046 1451
grid. They are a sum of calculated Legendre coefficients for      2046 1451
compound nucleus and shape-elastic scattering. For higher         2046 1451
incident energies, relative angular distributions are tabulated   2046 1451
on an angular grid.                                               2046 1451
                                                                  2046 1451
